ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上佢有葡國護照，已經贏哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06dd9cd64aa2861edb0bf2eb59133a371623f69","tid":1161760,"uid":118343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8a931bb9edd3a074e6bc2a44ff3663e3288960a","tid":1161760,"uid":100680,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e06dd9cd64aa2861edb0bf2eb59133a371623f69","tid":1161760,"uid":118343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"香港更加無人care<br />\n睇下你本護照先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0491c9f25ff2643576b9dc7a967fb41aba5f9a","tid":1161760,"uid":100680,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"4a6b0afbe2132583217251a8e38941e0da38eefe","tid":1161760,"uid":221460,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"評審準則唔只係唱的好唔好聽<br />\n會考慮埋首歌既本身既意義<br />\n同埋製作係咪認真 修音效果大細<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係針對邊個歌手<br />\n而係澳門暫時未有錄音水準高過台灣 香港既錄音技術<br />\n入圍唔到演唱類好正常<br />\n<br />\n而且製作偏低成本<br />\n自然入圍唔到製作獎項 (MV、製作人)<br />\n<br />\n順便一提 台灣宜家呢幾年入圍既都唔係普通芭樂歌<br />\n全部都係自己寫 (lala、艾宜良) 或者概念專輯 (阿密特) <br />\n或者生死、人生有關既歌<br />\n<br />\n澳門同香港撚寫到呢d歌咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"問題係而家澳門音樂已經進步左好多啦，我敢講質素係屌打而家香港幾條街<br />\n但係今年金曲獎仍然有唔少香港歌手有份玩<br />\n澳門歌手就無份玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我覺得台灣文化局係有心針對澳門歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f4281303550f5bc692295667f9c9f9d69bc85d","tid":1161760,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"508f843097c68ee8add7fc3fa02ba813a81e378e","tid":1161760,"uid":100680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac24e5094f0c046f1e958b38e50e136b9761c863","tid":1161760,"uid":13745,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"203d7e84c15ff840297c8a16